{"tid":314344,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【有圖】有冇人好掛住徐子珊","createTime":"2017-07-09T06:24:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-11T15:13:20.000Z","uid":14730,"like":112,"dislike":65,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cc39fdc10712f41653514e57721a18654a93ab78","tid":314344,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T06:24:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/09/142341_ebf4148e1f9b4decbf1548a9311d591f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F09%2F142341_ebf4148e1f9b4decbf1548a9311d591f.jpg&h=0787eae3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/09/142351_02b95cc3a11699eeb1a08adbfc4a7fd5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F09%2F142351_02b95cc3a11699eeb1a08adbfc4a7fd5.jpg&h=8f1f3ba9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/09/142357_29b63fe26bde1ea65b8973500107d5b6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F09%2F142357_29b63fe26bde1ea65b8973500107d5b6.jpg&h=2aa0e9fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n近期多位新世代演員在大台彈起的同時，大家又有沒有發現一些過去幾乎晚晚在電視見到的小生花旦，已經不再停留三色公仔箱的發展呢？憑「不死之身」聞名電視界的徐子珊自從在2015年約滿無線之後，一直消失香港觀眾的眼前，不過她去年簽約王祖藍和邵氏合作的工作室，順勢打入內地市場，同時又推出自家珠寶品牌，成為不折不扣的女強人。現年38歲的徐子珊確實比以往多了幾分女人味，愈來愈有個性。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2tZiirU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2tZiirU&d=3%2Ffu82qcZ4jJTgeXT1c27J7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=d025db99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2tZiirU</a>"},{"pid":"737d6ca3fa085d409a671376519f6c7c8fe362ea","tid":314344,"uid":3109,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T06:25:43.000Z","msg":"最少廿分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"960136da93d16e4c48ce240db0c9e369d8985163","tid":314344,"uid":90890,"like"